(59, '156ec411-ead6-46ae-b487-ed234ab64bbc', '175733b2-4266-4e6a-a2a1-d80c9d9b77a2', 'Single-page iOS app built with Flutter.', '<p>Before writing any code, my most important piece of advice when using AI coding tools is this: <strong>Always start by writing detailed and specific instructions.</strong> This dramatically increases the chances that the AI will produce the code you want and significantly reduces later refactoring.</p><p><br></p>', 1, '2025-10-22 18:55:24', '2025-10-22 18:55:46'),
